{"tid":226689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家】專訪郭文貴：美國之音內部 多人與北京有「複雜關係」","createTime":"2017-05-02T16:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T06:50:53.000Z","uid":30561,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed81589f161662a732a95bd9bb9344d6fdfb728","tid":226689,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170502/large/1493707876_767a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170502%2Flarge%2F1493707876_767a.jpg&h=a7b25b17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逃亡美國的中國富豪郭文貴早前接受美國之音（VOA）專訪，惟突然被腰斬，事件引發軒然大波。有海外中文媒體今日更揭露，多名參與專訪的人員，包括普通話部主任龔小夏、節目主持人東方、資深編輯李肅、寶申，及資深記者楊晨無限期休假，接受調查。消息傳出後，事件主角郭文貴接受《蘋果》獨家訪問，大爆美國之音的員工竟與北京安全情報外交有複雜關係，且類似情況「不是一兩個」。<br />\n<br />\n【美國之音大地震】徹查郭文貴專訪事件 警衞押停職編輯出大樓(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qyeQ2z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qyeQ2z&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=f15cd7fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qyeQ2z</a>)<br />\n【美國之音大地震】VOA大地震 郭文貴質疑能否查出真相(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2p3oRUT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p3oRUT&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=9fab3904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2p3oRUT</a>)<br />\n【美國之音大地震】千絲萬縷 最大醜聞背後誰是黑手？(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2p3JD6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p3JD6Q&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=7653b604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2p3JD6Q</a>)<br />\n【獨家】郭文貴爆中共在港有多個據點 銅鑼灣有安全屋專鎖人 (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2p118UG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p118UG&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b085d76b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2p118UG</a>)<br />\n【獨家】郭文貴足版爆料錄音曝光 聲稱傅政華「變聲」代習下令查王岐山 (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pTMpzJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pTMpzJ&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=48f169b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pTMpzJ</a>)<br />\n【十九大權鬥】郭文貴繼續爆 曝光王岐山與妻共有物業證據 （<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2p4XR7n）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p4XR7n%EF%BC%89&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=8115469d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2p4XR7n）</a><br />\n郭文貴說：「兩三天之間發生的事是我親身經歷的， 最可怕是他們（VOA）裏面，絕對不是一兩個，（而是）很多個跟北京安全情報外交各種複雜關係，北京用不惜一切代價的力量影響他們。我第一次聽張晶的名字，北京一個老領導說，他說：『張晶是我們的人。』這讓我很震驚。後來我問東方張晶的身份，東方透露張晶是個助理。後來老領導又表示，張晶的家好似是新華社的（人），人都在北京在控制之下，往好想他是因家人受威脅必須聼他們，但我聽口氣，張在北京安全部門很深的關係，他們相當尊重張晶、相信張晶的，所以這就複雜了。」<br />\n另外，知情人士亦對《明鏡郵報》說，此次直播中斷事件特別引人注目的是，遠東部助理兼亞太主編張晶的角色。這位先後畢業於北京大學、芝加哥大學的高材生，是首位《人民日報》駐華盛頓記者張彥之子。他被認為是具體命令中斷直播的領導者，但是他的決定是得到4名美國之音高層的支持。<br />\n《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"6d7956d670b7a824a09b974ce16c3efd48c0e365","tid":226689,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:28:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170502/56641513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170502%2F56641513&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=df7f582a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170502%2F56641513&h=b1d25404\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170502/56641513</a>"},{"pid":"9e422a8a66c2e24ba8585890931a574166a1541a","tid":226689,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ce99b820f0c467f2334f95fcbc691b42967b8d8","tid":226689,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"連美國之音都滲透到<br />\n<br />\n美國佬ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都請個支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi